### Key architectural decisions in this RAG layer

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| **Chroma per-tenant collections** | Hard isolation — different collection names, no cross-tenant queries possible |
| **Hybrid search (semantic + BM25)** | Semantic alone misses exact keyword matches; BM25 alone misses semantic similarity. Combined via Reciprocal Rank Fusion |
| **Cross-encoder reranking** | Re-scores top candidates for precision, critical when top-k is small |
| **Cosine similarity threshold** | Filters out low-relevance noise before reranking |
| **Citation keys in context** | Enables the LLM to cite sources, which can be verified downstream |
| **Grounding verification** | Automated check that the LLM's response is supported by retrieved chunks |
| **Embedding on CPU** | Saves GPU VRAM for the LLM; embeddings are fast enough on CPU |
| **Singleton pattern for models** | Avoids reloading models on every request |

